  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main objective of the study is to analyze the influence of several environmental (i.e.,
      timing: seasonal, circadian) and demographic conditions (i.e., age, gender, menstrual cycle)
      on anesthetic drug requirements (hypnotic and opiate).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
